articles.title: ICC World Cup 2023: Who’ll win New Zealand vs South Africa match? Prediction, fantasy team, pitch report and more | Mint - Mint
articles.description: New Zealand and South Africa will face off on a Big Match Day on November 1 in Pune. The Kiwis will be desperate to avoid a hat-trick of loss while the Proteas want to claim back the top position on the points table.
